creator: St. Virgil Salzburg
descriptionHtml:
Our app is the ideal companion for your stay in St. Virgil Salzburg. Download the app now!

AN A TO Z OF INFORMATION
Everything you need to know about our Education and Conference Centre St. Virgil Salzburg with hotel and gastronomy in Austria at a glance: Details about our range of conference, meeting and education offers, our events, the location map, arrival and departure options as well as our mission statement and sustainable business practices.

Virgil education, Virgil conference and Virgil gastronomy
Get inspired by upcoming lectures, seminars and conferences at our centre and find out what we have to offer. Are you planning an event and looking for the right premises? Simply send us your enquiries and requests via the app - we will get back to you as soon as possible.

Take a look at our sustainable hospitality in Salzburg with regional and organic cuisine. We would be happy to organise your personal celebration. We are easily accessible by public transport!

Virgil hotel
Discover the cultural and spiritual highlights of the World Heritage Site - the city of Salzburg - from Virgil's perspective! Our group offers are tailor-made and prepared for you by professionals. With the app you will always have our digital city map with the most important sights of Salzburg and tour recommendations at hand on your smartphone.

Here you will also find useful addresses and telephone numbers as well as information on public transport, the Salzburg Card, restaurant recommendations and much more.

Requests and news
Would you like to cancel room cleaning at the hotel or do you have any questions? Send us your request via the app or write us a message via the chat box.

You’ll receive the latest news as a push notification on your smartphone or tablet as well as via our Virgil magazine – that way you will always be up to date with what’s going on at St. Virgil Salzburg.

Book and rate your stay
Did you find your stay in our centre enriching? Is so, please let us know and why not request your next preferred date in the hotel, or for seminars or conferences right away!

Your opinion is important to us! We would be very pleased to receive your personal feedback on your stay at St. Virgil Salzburg. inspiring.continuing education.
